Group 4 Term Project 1


Creating a Mail Server OpenBSD 7.0 with Qemu on Vinet emulator.


Installing OpenBSD
----------------------

We first need to install openBSD. I have downloaded the 7.0 iso file from openBSD.org and then used sftp to get the file on the vinet server.

Using the QEMU Virtual machine manager I load the ISO and begin the installation process
Install process:

(I) for install
(us) for keyboard layout
tp1g4 hostname
