SSH is configured by OS installation so it works when connecting
via ip address.

Now disable login by root. Any root actions must be done with root
password.

Added the sudo package. placed sabinek,patalr, and hochom into the wheel group
and now the sudo command can be used to perform administrative tasks by the group.

Securing ssh with SSH keys

Installing required packages for our system;
